In the Matter of SHOREFRONT APARTMENTS, LLC, Respondent,
v.
Nella MANKO, Appellant, et al., Respondent. Motion No: 2017-1107 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided on January 9, 2018

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the Court of Appeals does not have jurisdiction to entertain it (see NY Const, art VI, § 3 ; CPLR 5602 ).

**579*802Motion for poor person relief dismissed as academic.
